@startuml secuencia-api-gateway
!theme plain
title Experimento 01 - Diagrama de Secuencia: Flujo de Peticion por Gateway

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
skinparam participantBorderColor #2980B9

actor "Cliente" as C
participant "Gateway\n(Nginx/Istio/Kong)" as GW
participant "api-service\n:8080" as API
participant "auth-service\n:8080" as AUTH
participant "data-service\n:8080" as DATA
database "PostgreSQL\n:5432" as PG

== Autenticacion (POST /login) ==

C -> GW : HTTPS POST /login\n{username, password}
GW -> AUTH : HTTP POST /login\n(TLS terminado en gateway)
AUTH -> PG : SELECT * FROM app_users\nWHERE username=?
PG --> AUTH : user record
AUTH --> GW : HTTP 200 {jwt_token}
GW --> C : HTTPS 200 {jwt_token}

== Solicitud de Perfil (GET /profile) ==

C -> GW : HTTPS GET /profile\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>
GW -> API : HTTP GET /profile\n(reescritura de path)
API -> AUTH : HTTP GET /validate\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>

alt Token valido
  AUTH --> API : HTTP 200 {user_info}
  API -> DATA : HTTP GET /users?id=1
  DATA -> PG : SELECT * FROM app_users WHERE id=1
  PG --> DATA : user record
  DATA --> API : HTTP 200 {user_data}
  API --> GW : HTTP 200 {profile_response}
  GW --> C : HTTPS 200 {profile_response}
else Token invalido
  AUTH --> API : HTTP 401 Unauthorized
  API --> GW : HTTP 401
  GW --> C : HTTPS 401 Unauthorized
end

== Diferencias por Configuracion ==

note over GW
  **Nginx**: Reescritura path /$2
  Clase ingress: nginx
  TLS terminado con Nginx cert

  **Istio**: VirtualService con match de URI
  Sidecar proxy en cada servicio
  TLS terminado con credencial Istio

  **Kong**: Anotaciones Kong en Ingress
  Rate-limiting disponible
  TLS terminado con Kong secret
end note

@enduml
